channel.title: Ekstrak’s Social Medias
channel.description:
So, I’mma start to be active on my Social Medias.
[My Instagram](https://www.instagram.com/iamekstrak/)
[My YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5n9FSgIaLkU5M7vHXhmxbg)
[My Bandlab (SoundCloud Alternative)](https://www.bandlab.com/ekstrakofficial)
My Discord Username: Username: !! Ekstrak !! Tag: #1685
[details="Details About My Accounts"] Instagram: I take *filtered* pictures of myself, memes, and previews of songs and their covers.
YouTube: I do gaming. I kinda post my music there; not anymore. What I usually post is racing games, usually Asphalt 8 or 9.
Bandlab: It’s basically my SoundCloud Alternative. What is Bandlab? It’s a SoundCloud Alternative where young music producers can start their career with a great way. Sponsor ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°) (jk)
Discord: It will be a rare occasion where you don’t see me online on Discord. I am hecka active there than anywhere else. [/details]
I’ll be more active there than here, at the Forums.
